Class RestAPIDbAdapter

java.lang.Object
  edu.uml.cs.isense.comm.RestAPIDbAdapter

public class RestAPIDbAdapter
extends java.lang.Object

Cached version of iSENSE Database to be used as a backup in case there is no connectivity. Version 2.0

Author:
iSENSE Android-Development Team including Mike Stowell, Nick Ver Voort, Jeremy Poulin, and James Dalphond
